<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Perfido - Reset Password Email</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;  margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password in Perfido.</p>
        <p>Your one-time password (OTP) code is: <strong>{{otpCode}}</strong></p>
        <p>Instruction for ignoring the email if the recipient didn't request a password reset.</p>
        <p>Thank you,</p>
        <p>The Perfido Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
